  "name": "RPlog_Hiring_the_Caterer",
  "title": "An Evening at Ruathen's",
  "summary": "The pompous Corellian noble Lord Geophreigh Smitherbodkins dines at the opulent restaurant Ruathen's with his put-upon Kubaz valet J'Eeves, planning an extravagant party meant to be the event of the century. Over rare brot-rib, Pikpik eggs, and Rimble wine served by the maitre'd Micar and his waiters, Smitherbodkins and J'Eeves work through the guest list, security arrangements, and catering details, relishing the prospect of mixing Imperial and New Republic guests under one roof. Meanwhile, a Rodian known as Daleth, a Hunter, meets briefly with the restaurant's proprietor Vyal to arrange covert transportation, and tips Vyal to watch the wealthy nobleman and his attentive bodyguard. Vyal works the room and ultimately approaches Smitherbodkins, who, delighted by the recognition of his house, commissions Ruathen's to cater his event. Vyal accepts the honor before excusing himself on urgent business, leaving Micar to attend the lord.",
